profile:
Since 2009, Canadoor Door Systems has been bringing professionalism to the garage door industry. To ensure we perform every job to the highest standard, whether you need a garage door repair or installation, our technicians undergo a rigorous training process until we’re confident they are ready to enter the field.

We provide service across Ontario, with showrooms in Thunder Bay, Sudbury, Barrie, and Bolton, where you can meet our team and browse our selection of garage doors. Whether you’re a homeowner in need of a garage door repair, new installation or a business looking for preventative maintenance on your commercial properties, we can help.
